msgid ""
"Returns a node path with a colon character (``:``) prepended, "
"transforming it to a pure property path with no node name (defaults to "
"resolving from the current node)."
msgstr "返回带有冒号（``:``）的节点路径，将其转换为没有节点名称的纯属性路径（默认为从当前节点解析）。"

