msgstr ":ref:`String <class_String>` **get_concatenated_subnames** **(** **)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_nodepath.rst:111
msgid ""
"Returns all subnames concatenated with a colon character (``:``) as "
"separator, i.e. the right side of the first colon in a node path."
msgstr "返回所有用冒号（``:``）分隔的子名称，即节点路径中第一个冒号的右侧部分。"

