#: ../../docs/classes/class_nodepath.rst:163
msgid ""
"Gets the number of resource or property names (\"subnames\") in the path."
" Each subname is listed after a colon character (``:``) in the node path."
msgstr "获取路径中资源或属性名称（``子名称``）的数量。每个子名称在节点路径中的冒号（``:``）之后列出。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_nodepath.rst:165
msgid ""
"For example, ``\"Path2D/PathFollow2D/Sprite:texture:load_path\"`` has 2 "
"subnames."
msgstr "例如，``\"Path2D/PathFollow2D/Sprite:texture:load_path\"`` 具有2个子名称。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_nodepath.rst:171
msgid ":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **is_absolute** **(** **)**"
msgstr ":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **is_absolute** **(** **)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_nodepath.rst:173
msgid ""
"Returns ``true`` if the node path is absolute (as opposed to relative), "
"which means that it starts with a slash character (``/``). Absolute node "
"paths can be used to access the root node (``\"/root\"``) or autoloads "
"(e.g. ``\"/global\"`` if a \"global\" autoload was registered)."
msgstr ""
"如果节点路径是绝对路径，则返回 ``true`` "
"（相对路径则相反），这意味着它以斜杠字符（``/``）开头。绝对节点路径可用于访问根节点（``\"/root\"``）或自动加载（例如，如果已注册一个"
" ``global`` 自动加载，则为 ``\"/global\"``）。"

