msgstr ":ref:`bool <class_bool>` **is_empty** **(** **)**"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_nodepath.rst:181
msgid "Returns ``true`` if the node path is empty."
msgstr "如果节点路径为空，则返回 ``true``。"

